{"tid":1383991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再吹奏劉細良啦","createTime":"2019-07-29T21:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T05:03:33.000Z","uid":161592,"like":238,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"b5fda82c469f9a77f7ca7c007a7f6529b8b5f073","tid":1383991,"uid":161592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T21:59:09.000Z","msg":"當初大家想要既係咩<br />\n就係唔想要大台 唔想要領袖 唔想比人代表 唔想比人騎劫<br />\n但好明顯呢一兩日有大量吹奏劉細良既post <br />\n而連登就開始慢慢吹和風 想大家見好就收<br />\n我想講既係 <br />\n唔通今時今日呢個情況 仲可以見好就收 靜觀其變咩？<br />\n<br />\n我可以幻想到如果我地係呢一刻收手 <br />\n大家會有咩下場<br />\n將會被打壓 被秋後算帳 政府 警隊更加橫行無道<br />\n<br />\n我想大家認真諗一諗<br />\n自己想要啲咩 想爭取啲咩 <br />\n唔好咁容易比人影響到你既意念"},{"pid":"8370e3eb4b862576741552e8baf293e71cb7dd82","tid":1383991,"uid":161592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T22:00:26.000Z","msg":"求下你地認真思考下"},{"pid":"fab88c516ecf2535f48a38eaaf72b65ed220e3e9","tid":1383991,"uid":58841,"like":44,"dislike":3,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T22:01:47.000Z","msg":"你理撚得細唔細良姐<br />\n佢俾D POINT你你唔識分岩定錯架"},{"pid":"4733073e338a9bc588ea4856f31e09323b559bd4","tid":1383991,"uid":161592,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"fab88c516ecf2535f48a38eaaf72b65ed220e3e9","tid":1383991,"uid":58841,"like":44,"dislike":3,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T22:01:47.000Z","msg":"你理撚得細唔細良姐<br />\n佢俾D POINT你你唔識分岩定錯架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T22:02:43.000Z","msg":"我意思係唔好一味盲目吹奏"},{"pid":"352884202909ac2bff88d3c56fe758c2cb145905","tid":1383991,"uid":130121,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"4733073e338a9bc588ea4856f31e09323b559bd4","tid":1383991,"uid":161592,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"fab88c516ecf2535f48a38eaaf72b65ed220e3e9","tid":1383991,"uid":58841,"like":44,"dislike":3,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T22:01:47.000Z","msg":"你理撚得細唔細良姐<br />\n佢俾D POINT你你唔識分岩定錯架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T22:02:43.000Z","msg":"我意思係唔好一味盲目吹奏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T22:06:1